nodes.text: Hunet L'Beck was a male Bimm bureaucrat who served the senator of Bimmisaari in the Galactic Republic during the Cold War.

In 3643 BBY, he invited Ula Vii to dinner in order to learn more about the background of Lema Xandret and Cinzia Xandret. L'Beck told him that the the Senate Office of Bimmisaari had received an offer from the Hutts, which would be auctioned on Nal Hutta of the NaviComputer and an artifact of the wrecked Cinzia.
